        <headline>Severe Thunderstorm Warning issued June 2 at 3:03PM CDT until June 2 at 3:30PM CDT by NWS Amarillo TX</headline>
        <description>At 303 PM CDT, automated weather equipment reported a severe
thunderstorm was located 4 miles north of Dalhart, moving north at 25
mph.

HAZARD...60 mph wind gusts and half dollar size hail.

SOURCE...Automated weather equipment.

IMPACT...Minor damage to roofs, siding, and trees is possible. Hail
damage to vehicles is expected.

Locations impacted include...
Dalhart.
</description>
        <instruction>For your protection move to an interior room on the lowest floor of a
building.</instruction>
